import React from 'react';
import Link from 'next/Link'

import {
  ProgramName,
  FieldHeader,
  FieldValue,
  Container,
  CollegeName,
  Logo,
} from './ProgramRow.styles';



const ProgramRow = ({program: {school, degreeType, deliveryMode, name, id}}) => {

  console.log(school)

  return(
    <Link href={`/programDetail?id=${id}`} as={`/programDetail/${name}`}>
      <Container >
        <Logo/>
        <ProgramName>{name}</ProgramName>
        <CollegeName>{}</CollegeName>
        <FieldHeader start={4} end={5}>
          Degree Type
        </FieldHeader>
        <FieldValue start={4} end={5}>
          {degreeType}
        </FieldValue>
        <FieldHeader start={5} end={6}>
          Delivery
        </FieldHeader>
        <FieldValue start={5} end={6}>
          {deliveryMode}
        </FieldValue>
        <FieldHeader start={6} end={7}>
          Annual Tuition
        </FieldHeader>
        <FieldValue start={6} end={7}>
          $1,375
        </FieldValue>
      </Container>
    </Link>

  )


};

export default ProgramRow;
